<p>Hello <%= @resource.name %>!</p>

<p>Someone has requested a link to change your password on <a href="https://LetsAdvance.io">LetsAdvance.io</a>. You can do this using the link below.</p>

<p><%= link_to 'Change Password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token) %></p>

<p>If you did not request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p>Your password will not change unless you use the provided link.</p>